data.description: Motivated Sellers! Move in Ready! VA Assumable loan at 3.5%! NO HOA! On Greenbelt which means NO backyard neighbors! Welcome Home! This single story home located in Tuscany Meadows has all you need to entertain. The large foyer invites you inside this beautiful open floorplan and into the large eat-in kitchen with its unlimited cabinet space and sleek granite countertops, along with both a kitchen island and breakfast bar perfect for eating and entertaining everyone. The high ceilings throughout the home create a spacious feeling along with plenty of natural lighting throughout the homes interior! Split bedrooms allow both guest bedrooms to be on your right as you enter the home and separates the large master suite with a walk in closet toward the exterior of the home. The master bath features dual vanities along with a separate garden tub and walk in shower that is perfect for cooling off in this Texas heat. The patio in backyard has been extended to allow more area to entertain, along with gate access down to Trimmer creek and a shed for extra storage space. Sprinkler system installed and the lot is full of mature trees and endless possibilities! Playset in backyard conveys with the home. Minutes away from shopping, restaurants, parks, and Stillhouse Lake! 20 minutes to Ft Cavazos(Ft Hood). Schedule your showing today!
